an incredibly rich tradition.

00:03:24.260 --> 00:03:28.100 align:middle line:84%
So there's practices relating to
the body, relating to the mind,

00:03:28.100 --> 00:03:30.530 align:middle line:84%
relating to the
imagination, relating

00:03:30.530 --> 00:03:34.410 align:middle line:84%
to the faculty of attention,
