00:04:43.910 --> 00:04:46.970 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, that's a long story.

00:04:46.970 --> 00:04:48.830 align:middle line:84%
There's actually
quite a few scholars

00:04:48.830 --> 00:04:51.740 align:middle line:84%
working on that
very issue, what's

00:04:51.740 --> 00:04:53.960 align:middle line:84%
called the mediation or
transmission of Tantra

00:04:53.960 --> 00:04:57.290 align:middle line:84%
