the last 120 years,

00:04:57.290 --> 00:05:01.100 align:middle line:84%
and how it's resulted in a
variety of misunderstandings.

00:05:01.100 --> 00:05:04.400 align:middle line:84%
The biggest one being that most
people, when they hear the word

00:05:04.400 --> 00:05:06.980 align:middle line:84%
Tantra, think it's,
